page.name: The Joyful Mysteries
page.content:
The Joyful Mysteries

Monday, Saturday, Sundays of Advent

  1. The Annunciation - Gabriel announces to Mary (Luke 1:26-38)
  2. The Visitation - Mary visits Elizabeth (Luke 1:39-56)
  3. The Nativity - Jesus is born (Luke 2:1-20)
  4. The Presentation - Jesus presented in Temple (Luke 2:22-38)
  5. The Finding in the Temple - Jesus found teaching (Luke 2:41-52)
